body_html: @akaitsuki-ii so I tried making a timeline for your stuff (yaroslavvb/stuff@5d2feff), and I couldn't because your execution graph is too large. There are 942,316 ops being executed in the first session.run call. The dump of stepstats is over a GB and timeline generation chokes. So I think that's the real problem, and the "enqueue" op being slow is a false positive since tensorboard couldn't parse all the ops
